sequenceDiagram
    participant OP as Operator
    participant WEB as Web UI
    participant BASTION as Bastion
    participant COAP as CoAP Server
    participant FC1 as FC-1
    participant DCU as DCU

    OP->>WEB: Click "Connect to DCU"
    WEB->>BASTION: POST /api/v1/devices/{sn}/phone-home
    BASTION->>COAP: POST /api/v1/remote-access/trigger/{sn}
    COAP->>FC1: CoAP POST /remote_call_home/{can_sn}<br/>(over DTLS)

    Note over FC1: CoAP handler sets<br/>dcu_phonehome_triggered flag
    FC1->>FC1: Generate 8-byte nonce<br/>Compute HMAC-SHA256

    FC1->>DCU: DoIP RoutineControl 0x31<br/>routineId 0xF0A0<br/>[nonce + HMAC + bastion_host:port]

    DCU->>DCU: Verify HMAC<br/>Check replay cache<br/>Validate hostname
    DCU-->>FC1: Positive Response 0x71<br/>(routineRunning)

    DCU->>DCU: Fork phonehome-connect.sh

    DCU->>BASTION: SSH reverse tunnel<br/>-R 10008:localhost:22<br/>tunnel@bastion

    Note over BASTION: Tunnel port 10008 active

    WEB->>BASTION: GET /tunnel-status
    BASTION-->>WEB: status: connected, port: 10008

    OP->>BASTION: SSH -p 10008 greg@localhost
    BASTION->>DCU: Forward through reverse tunnel
    DCU-->>OP: Shell prompt
